videos.description: Penn State got its revenge on Michigan from last year's game as the Nittany Lions rolled past the Wolverines in a 42-13 victory. Trace McSorley threw for 282 yards, three rushing touchdowns and one passing score. Meanwhile Saquon Barkley had 176 all purpose yards with three total touchdowns.
videos.title: College Football: Penn State lights up Michigan
